# Literals and value printing
5
=> 5
-3
=> -3
0
=> 0
1.5
=> 1.5
1.0
=> 1
3.14
=> 3.14
1e3
=> 1000
2.5e-1
=> 0.25
true
=> true
false
=> false
"hello"
=> "hello"
"a b c"
=> "a b c"
2i
=> 2i
3 + 4i
=> 3+4i
0 + 2i
=> 2i
1:5
=> [1, 2, 3, 4, 5]
1:2:9
=> [1, 3, 5, 7, 9]
5:-1:1
=> [5, 4, 3, 2, 1]
2:1
=> []
